      <title>几乎没有人会做空国债。也许他们应该是</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/hardly-anyone-is-short-treasuries-perhaps-they-should-be-luldp2pb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[调查数据显示，美国国债的直接空头数量已接近低点。但投资者错过了一个窍门，因为通胀风险表明债券波动性和收益率更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/hardly-anyone-is-short-treasuries-perhaps-they-should-be-luldp2pb</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
