      <title>津巴布韦新任央行行长的任务是解决 77% 的货币崩溃问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/usd-zwl-news-zimbabwe-central-banker-tasked-to-fix-77-currency-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦新任央行行长约翰·穆沙亚万胡 (John Mushayavanhu) 面临着一项艰巨的任务：恢复这个以印刷 100 万亿美元钞票和 200% 利率而不是连贯货币政策而闻名的机构的信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/usd-zwl-news-zimbabwe-central-banker-tasked-to-fix-77-currency-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:07:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新研究发现，扣除费用后，私人信贷不会带来额外收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/private-credit-offers-no-extra-gains-after-fees-new-study-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位学者对蓬勃发展的 1.7 万亿美元私人信贷市场做出了大胆的看法：在考虑了额外的风险和费用后，该资产类别几乎没有为投资者带来额外的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/private-credit-offers-no-extra-gains-after-fees-new-study-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:53:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
